<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA73">
<l>pukaḻvāy paḻippāynī pūntuḻā yāṉai</l>
<l>yikaḻvāy karutuvā yeṉṉeñcē – tikaḻnīrk</l>
<l>kaṭalu malaiyu miruvicumpuṅ kāṟṟu</l>
<l>muṭalu muyirumēṟ ṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You praise, you blame, you slight , you ponder</l>
<l>him with the flowering tulsi, my heart – him</l>
<l>who held the sea, the mountain, the vast sky,</l>
<l>the wind, the bodies and [their life] breaths.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
